### 🌍 Variables globales
@host = 54.173.187.8
@id = 123456-test              # variable temporal para test de PUT/DELETE

### 🚀 1. Create a new Bitcoin position
POST http://{{host}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.25,
  "type": "buy",
  "date": "2025-10-12"
}

### 📋 2. Get all positions
GET http://{{host}}/items

### 🔍 3. Get position by ID
# 🟡 Reemplaza {{id}} con un ID real obtenido del GET anterior
GET http://{{host}}/items/{{id}}

### ✏️ 4. Update position by ID
PUT http://{{host}}/items/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "quantity": 0.5,
  "type": "sell",
  "date": "2025-10-13"
}

### ❌ 5. Delete position by ID
DELETE http://{{host}}/items/{{id}}

### 🧭 6. Swagger Documentation (UI)
GET http://{{host}}/docs

### 🏠 7. Frontend (HTML interface)
GET http://{{host}}/

### 🛠️ 8. Health Check
GET http://{{host}}/health
